@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
actor Maker
actor Taker
rectangle "Escrow Program\n(signs as escrow PDA)" as Prog
usecase "make" as Make
usecase "take" as Take
usecase "refund\n(expiry-gated)" as Refund
Maker --> Make : signs
Taker --> Take : signs
Maker ..> Refund : fee payer only
Prog --> Take : invoke_signed
Prog --> Refund : invoke_signed
@enduml
